---
// W-1 Landing (docs/14 §W-1 + docs/09 §1). Metinler docs/09 §1 iskeletinden; P-1 cilası
// Ahmet onayı ile finalize edilir. Renkler yalnız tokens.css değişkenlerinden (QA: hex yok).
import '../../styles/tokens.css';
// Ödeme YALNIZ mağaza içi (App Store / Google Play) — webde satış yok (docs/06 §5).
const FOUNDING_LIST = 'mailto:hello@kerfkit.app?subject=Founding%20list'; // KARAR: Buttondown (docs/14) — Ahmet hesabı açınca embed-subscribe formuna çevrilecek; isim geçişi (docs/NAME.md: KerfKit) aynı PR'da
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>KerfKit — cut list optimizer. One-time price, yours forever.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="KerfKit: cut list optimizer for woodworkers. 2D panel + 1D linear optimization, workshop mode, fully offline. One-time $49 founding price — no subscription. Ever." />
</head>
<body>

<header class="kabuk">
  <div class="marka">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="28" height="28" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="1024" height="1024" fill="var(--color-timber-900)" rx="230"/><g fill="var(--color-amber-500)" transform="rotate(-45 512 512)"><rect x="-300" y="342" width="788" height="340"/><rect x="536" y="342" width="788" height="340"/></g></svg>
    <span>kerfkit</span>
  </div>
  <a class="cta cta-sm" href={FOUNDING_LIST}>Join the founding list</a>
</header>

<main>
  <!-- Hero — docs/09 §1 başlık iskeleti birebir -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-metin">
      <h1>Stop paying monthly<br/>to cut plywood.</h1>
      <p class="alt-baslik">One-time <strong>$49</strong>, yours forever. No subscription. Ever.</p>
      <p class="founding-satir">
        Founding price — first 300 seats (<span id="sayac" data-endpoint="/founding.json">real counter</span>), then $99.99.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href={FOUNDING_LIST}>Join the founding list — lock in $49</a>
      <p class="magaza-notu">Payment happens in-app at launch — <strong>App Store</strong> &amp; <strong>Google Play</strong>. No card forms here, ever.</p>
      <p class="uyum-notu">Prices include VAT where applicable · Store refund policies apply, plus our 14-day support promise · Founding counter reads real launch sales data.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Canlı mini-demo: GERÇEK motor çıktısı (11 parçalık dolap projesi; 1 levha,
         %19,3 fire, 20 kesim — CutCore v0.1.0-dev, kerf 3mm). docs/11 §5: sahte veri yok. -->
    <figure class="demo">
      <svg viewBox="-8 -8 626 321" role="img" aria-label="Cut plan diagram: 11 cabinet parts optimized onto one 2440 by 1220 plywood sheet, 19.3 percent waste">
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="610" height="305" fill="var(--color-timber-800)" stroke="var(--color-timber-700)" stroke-width="2"/>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.05s"><rect x="0" y="114" width="140" height="191" /><text x="70" y="212">Shelf</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.15s"><rect x="140.75" y="114" width="140" height="191"/><text x="210" y="212">Shelf</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.25s"><rect x="281.5" y="160" width="180" height="145"/><text x="371" y="235">Side</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.35s"><rect x="281.5" y="14.25" width="180" height="145"/><text x="371" y="90">Side</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.45s"><rect x="462.25" y="126" width="99" height="179"/><text x="511" y="218">Door</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.55s"><rect x="562" y="206" width="45" height="99"/><text x="584" y="258" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.65s"><rect x="0" y="14.25" width="45" height="99"/><text x="22" y="66" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.75s"><rect x="45.75" y="14.25" width="45" height="99"/><text x="68" y="66" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.85s"><rect x="91.5" y="14.25" width="45" height="99"/><text x="114" y="66" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:0.95s"><rect x="140.75" y="14.25" width="45" height="99"/><text x="163" y="66" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
        <g class="parca" style="--d:1.05s"><rect x="186.5" y="14.25" width="45" height="99"/><text x="209" y="66" class="mini">Dr</text></g>
      </svg>
      <figcaption>Real engine output — 11 parts · 1 sheet · 19.3% waste · 20 cuts</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <!-- Nasıl çalışır — 3 adım -->
  <section class="adimlar">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Enter your cut list.</strong> Parts, quantities, grain direction. Metric or fractional inches — 10 parts in under a minute.</li>
      <li><strong>Get the optimal plan.</strong> Guillotine-safe layouts your panel saw can actually cut, kerf and trim accounted for, deterministic every time.</li>
      <li><strong>Cut in workshop mode.</strong> Big type, screen stays awake, tap each cut as you go. Sawdust-friendly.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <!-- Dürüst karşılaştırma (docs/02 esası; isim W-4'te) -->
  <section class="kiyas">
    <h2>Why not the web-based subscription optimizers?</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th></th><th>Subscription optimizers</th><th>KerfKit</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Price</td><td>$5–15 every month, forever</td><td>One-time $49 founding ($99.99 after)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Works offline in the shop</td><td>Mostly no — browser required</td><td>Yes — fully offline, your data stays on device</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Workshop mode at the saw</td><td>No</td><td>Big-type step-by-step cut list</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2D panels + 1D linear stock</td><td>Usually separate tools</td><td>Both, one app</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cloud sync across devices</td><td>Yes — their strong suit</td><td>v1: on-device (iCloud sync on the roadmap)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="dipnot">Honest table: sync is genuinely their advantage today. We'd rather ship offline-first and add sync than the reverse.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Fiyat — docs/08 §1 yapısı -->
  <section class="fiyat" id="pricing">
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <div class="kutular">
      <div class="kutu">
        <h3>Free</h3>
        <p class="rakam">$0</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited calculations — no counter, ever</li>
          <li>2 saved projects, 20 parts each</li>
          <li>Full diagram view</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="kutu one-cikan">
        <p class="rozet">Founding — 300 seats</p>
        <h3>Lifetime</h3>
        <p class="rakam">$49 <span class="sonra">then $99.99</span></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything, forever, on this platform</li>
          <li>Unlimited projects &amp; parts</li>
          <li>PDF/CSV export, full workshop mode</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="cta" href={FOUNDING_LIST}>Get notified at launch</a>
      </div>
      <div class="kutu">
        <h3>Yearly</h3>
        <p class="rakam">$39.99<span class="sonra">/year</span></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything while active</li>
          <li>Renewal date always visible</li>
          <li>Weekend pass also available — $4.99 / 72h, never auto-renews</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SSS -->
  <section class="sss">
    <h2>Questions, answered straight</h2>
    <dl>
      <dt>What if it's not for me?</dt>
      <dd>Refunds go through the App Store / Google Play, and we back them with a 14-day support promise — email us and we'll make it right.</dd>
      <dt>How do I pay?</dt>
      <dd>In the app, through the App Store or Google Play. This site never asks for a card.</dd>
      <dt>Which platforms?</dt>
      <dd>iOS first (launching now), Android next, web lite calculator free in your browser. Founding license covers the platform you buy on — pricing parity promise across platforms.</dd>
      <dt>Does it work offline?</dt>
      <dd>Completely. Your cut lists never leave your device. No account required.</dd>
      <dt>Is the counter real?</dt>
      <dd>Yes — it reads live sales data. No fake countdowns, no fake scarcity. When 300 seats are gone, the price is $99.99.</dd>
      <dt>Subscription trap?</dt>
      <dd>Lifetime means lifetime. The yearly and weekend options exist for people who prefer them — the weekend pass never auto-renews.</dd>
    </dl>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="kabuk alt">
  <p>© 2026 KerfKit · <a href="mailto:hello@kerfkit.app">hello@kerf.app</a> · answers within 24 hours</p>
  <p><a href="#">Privacy</a> · <a href="#">Refund policy</a> · <a href="#">Terms</a></p>
  <p class="duvar">Founding Craftsmen wall — beta members appear here (with permission).</p>
</footer>

<script>
  // Founding sayacı — GERÇEK veri (docs/09 §1: sahte kıtlık yok). Stub: /founding.json.
  const el = document.getElementById('sayac');
  fetch(el.dataset.endpoint).then(r => r.json()).then(d => {
    el.textContent = `${d.seats - d.claimed} of ${d.seats} left`;
  }).catch(() => { el.textContent = '300 seats'; });
</script>

<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--color-timber-950); color: var(--color-timber-200);
    font: 17px/1.6 -apple-system, "SF Pro Text", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  }
  main { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  h1, h2, h3 { color: var(--color-timber-50); line-height: 1.15; }
  h2 { font-size: 28px; margin: 72px 0 24px; }
  a { color: var(--color-amber-400); }

  .kabuk { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
           padding: 16px 24px; max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .marka { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 700;
           font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: .02em; color: var(--color-timber-50); }

  .cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--color-amber-500); color: var(--color-text-onAccent);
         font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 10px; }
  .cta:hover { background: var(--color-amber-400); }
  .cta-sm { padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 14px; }

  .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center;
          padding: 64px 0 32px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 44px; }
  .alt-baslik { font-size: 21px; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
  .alt-baslik strong { color: var(--color-amber-400); }
  .founding-satir { color: var(--color-timber-300); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  #sayac { color: var(--color-amber-400); font-weight: 600; }
  .magaza-notu { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-timber-300); margin-top: 12px; }
  .uyum-notu { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-timber-500); margin-top: 14px; max-width: 46ch; }

  .demo svg { width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .demo figcaption { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-timber-300); margin-top: 8px; text-align: center; }
  .parca rect { fill: var(--color-amber-500); stroke: var(--color-timber-950); stroke-width: 1;
                opacity: 0; animation: belir .5s ease var(--d) forwards; }
  .parca text { fill: var(--color-text-onAccent); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
                text-anchor: middle; opacity: 0; animation: belir .5s ease calc(var(--d) + .2s) forwards; }
  .parca .mini { font-size: 10px; }
  @keyframes belir { to { opacity: 1; } }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .parca rect, .parca text { animation: none; opacity: 1; } }

  .adimlar ol { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;
                list-style: none; counter-reset: adim; padding: 0; }
  .adimlar li { background: var(--color-timber-900); border: 1px solid var(--color-timber-800);
                border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; counter-increment: adim; }
  .adimlar li::before { content: counter(adim); display: block; width: 34px; height: 34px;
                        border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-amber-500);
                        color: var(--color-text-onAccent); font-weight: 800;
                        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .adimlar strong { color: var(--color-timber-50); display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }

  .kiyas table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  .kiyas th, .kiyas td { text-align: left; padding: 12px 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-timber-800); }
  .kiyas thead th { color: var(--color-timber-300); font-size: 14px; border: 0; }
  .kiyas td:last-child { color: var(--color-timber-50); }
  .dipnot { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-timber-500); margin-top: 10px; }

  .kutular { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .kutu { background: var(--color-timber-900); border: 1px solid var(--color-timber-800);
          border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px; }
  .kutu.one-cikan { border-color: var(--color-amber-500); position: relative; }
  .rozet { position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 24px; background: var(--color-amber-500);
           color: var(--color-text-onAccent); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
           padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; }
  .rakam { font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-timber-50); margin: 10px 0 14px; }
  .sonra { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-timber-300); margin-left: 6px; }
  .kutu ul { padding-left: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .kutu li { margin: 8px 0; }

  .sss dl { max-width: 72ch; }
  .sss dt { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-timber-50); margin-top: 20px; }
  .sss dd { margin: 6px 0 0; color: var(--color-timber-300); }

  footer.alt { flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; align-items: flex-start;
               color: var(--color-timber-500); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 88px;
               border-top: 1px solid var(--color-timber-800); padding-top: 24px; padding-bottom: 48px; }
  .duvar { font-size: 12px; }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding-top: 32px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 34px; }
    .adimlar ol, .kutular { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</body>
</html>
